<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {{
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }}

        .email-container {{
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }}

        .header {{
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }}

        .header h1 {{
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }}

        .content {{
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }}

        .content h2 {{
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }}

        .content p {{
            margin: 10px 0;
        }}

        .content a {{
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }}

        .content a:hover {{
            text-decoration: underline;
        }}

        .cta-button {{
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none !important;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }}

        .cta-button:hover {{
            background-color: #45a049;
        }}

        .footer {{
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }}

        .footer a {{
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }}

        .emoji {{
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }}

        .highlight-box {{
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }}

        @media (max-width: 600px) {{
            .content h2 {{
                font-size: 18px;
            }}

            .header h1 {{
                font-size: 20px;
            }}

            .cta-button {{
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }}
        }}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1><span class="emoji">üå∫</span> MyST Build Completed! <span class="emoji">üå∫</span></h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2><span class="emoji">üßê</span> PREVIEW <span class="emoji">üßê</span></h2>

            <p>Great news! Your MyST build has been completed successfully.</p>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{preview_url}" class="cta-button">
                    <span class="emoji">üå±</span> View Your Living Preprint
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p><strong><span class="emoji">üëã</span> Important Reminder:</strong></p>
                <p>Remember to take a look at the <a href="{build_logs_url}">build logs</a> to check if all the notebooks have been executed successfully, as well as other warnings and errors from the MyST build.</p>
            </div>

            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for using our MyST build service!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>